  10. prime, 14. 29 across times 21 down ...). 
  """
 
  Also, see 
  http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cross-figure
  
  William Y. Sit: "On Crossnumber Puzzles and The Lucas-Bonaccio Farm 1998
  http://scisun.sci.ccny.cuny.edu/~wyscc/CrossNumber.pdf
  
