  17 _  18 19 X  20 21 _ 22    6
  _  X  23 _  X  24 _  X  _    7
  25 26 X  27 _  _  X  28 _    8
  29 _  _  _  X  30 _  _  _    9

 
  The answer is
   1608 9183
   60 201 42
   3 72 14 1
   5360 2866
